Description:
Surprisingly Spacious
An impressive combination of optimal location paired with the charming presence of this generous three bedroom, two bathroom townhouse inspires an impressive lifestyle. The expansive floorplan displays multi-functional living zones including a sun enhanced family room, upstairs retreat and spacious lounge combined with the impressive kitchen and meals area overlooking a quaint private courtyard with built in BBQ. An additional front entrance opens into the dining/study or possible fourth bedroom, a king size master suite comprises of an engaging ensuite and walk in robe, with mirrored built in robes enhancing two further bedrooms. In addition there is ducted heating, cooling and split system, ceiling fans, downstairs toilet and a single garage secluded by high fencing. Within moments to freeway access allows an easy commute to the CBD. Stroll to local amenities such as Keilor Village, sporting facilities including the bowling club, Library and community hub and a variety of both public and private schools. A brilliant home/investment in a highly sought after location.

Description:
Modern Lifestyle Winner In Elite Address
Displaying an immaculate countenance, this three bedroom, two bathroom home is situated on a premier corner allotment close to Keilor Village shops, public transport, parks, prestige schools and freeway access. Polished floorboards team with a timeless neutral palette throughout this refurbished delight, offering an easy care lifestyle for busy modern professionals. On entry, a unique gallery-style hall creates a compelling entree to lavish living spaces, with wraparound lounge and dining rooms seamlessly connecting to combined kitchen/meals. A raised, decked alfresco area set against a backdrop of established landscaped gardens sets a peaceful scene for outdoor entertaining. Lovely bedrooms include master with walk-through-robe and fully tiled ensuite; the central bathroom provides shower and bath. Includes secure parking, alarm, ducted heating, cooling, privacy blinds, water tank, garden shed. This rare beauty is sure to create a lasting impression.

Description:
Quiet Pocket In Sought-After Neighbourhood
Offering a sophisticated low maintenance lifestyle, this meticulously maintained three bedroom plus study/4th bedroom home set in landscaped gardens enjoys a premier setting within a serenely quiet court location. Delivering relaxed carefree living, the residence presents charismatic style throughout with polished floorboards and a soothing palette to enrich the senses. Upon entry, a welcoming alcove opens through French doors to a sizable lounge graced by a warming wood-fuelled heater. The adjoining kitchen/dining/family area - well appointed with tiled splashback, 600mm cooking appliances and dishwasher flows to an undercover decked alfresco entertaining area overlooking an inviting salt-chlorinated, solar-heated pool. Generous double-sized bedrooms all include built-in-robes and are well serviced by the central bathroom with double vanity, separate bath and shower. The property includes a dual access garage, carport, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, and split system air conditioning. Conveniently positioned close to bus service, train station, Calder Freeway access, St Augustines and Overnewton College, Brimbank park, and Keilor Village.

Description:
Precise Presentation In Coveted Keilor Locale
This charming four bedroom, two bathroom family home is enviably located close to Keilor Village shops, public transport, parklands, prestige schools (including Overnewton); and freeway access. Delightful manicured gardens hint at the timeless elegance found within; a considered single-level layout allowing for every comfort and convenience. A lovely tiled entry foyer pivots to the spacious formal lounge and dining areas, wrapping to a modernised kitchen with tiled splashback, dishwasher and 600mm cooktop. An additional living room opens to a sizeable undercover alfresco entertaining area, fitted with an indulgent six-person spa. The master bedroom - with walk-in-robe and ensuite - is placed in a separate wing to the remaining bedrooms, all fitted with built-in-robes and serviced by the main bathroom with bath/shower and separate toilet. One bedroom opens through glass sliders to the trim, established rear gardens. The property also features side access with a drive-through remote controlled garage, 2nd double garage/workshop, CCTV security and alarm, zoned ducted heating, and water tank.

Description:
Expansive Living - Picturesque Views
Capturing majestic views of Green Gully Valley, and featuring three generous living zones, this multi-level home is designed for a variety of family needs. Stunning leadlight entry, enticing L shaped lounge and dining, bright plus spacious family and meals area complete with wood heater provide family harmony. Extensive gourmet kitchen showcasing stone benchtops, stainless appliances including 900 gas cooktop and range, fan forced wall oven/grill and dishwasher cater for the entertainer. The separate downstairs rumpus leads to the covered alfresco, providing the perfect entertaining area, overlooking picturesque Taylors Creek. Displaying three double bedrooms plus a study/fourth bedroom, each maintaining built in robes, stunning fully tiled ensuite to master, plus two outstanding fully renovated bathrooms and separate powder room. Further enhancements to this well appointed property include double integrated remote garage, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ceiling fans and alarm. All within walking distance to Overnewton College, St Augustines, Keilor Village with fine eateries and specialty shops, parks and sporting facilities. Access to freeways and Ring road allows for easy city commute.

Description:
Timeless Magnificence With Premium Proportions
Exclusively situated seconds from Keilor Village is a magnificent four bedroom, four bathroom builders own family residence on approx. 1016m2, of unrivalled opulence, craftsmanship and scale. Exquisite in every detail, and uniquely designed, the property boasts a ten car basement garage with workshop/storerooms and direct home entry. A brilliant open plan living domain opens to all-weather alfresco entertaining zones featuring outdoor kitchen and mosaic-tiled, heated in-ground pool/spa with stacked-stone water feature. In addition, flawlessly designed living and entertaining areas unite on a spectacular scale and comprise a grand entry, fully equipped home theatre, dedicated study, games room/wet bar, elevated family retreat and gallery with balcony access. Showcasing contemporary finishes, such as cascading stone benches, 900mm live cooker, Siemens dishwasher, sleek cabinetry and walk-in-pantry, the kitchen is high end. All four bedrooms enjoy opulent ensuites and walk-in-robes, including an indulgent master with luxury spa. Features refrigerated cooling/ducted heating/vacuum, home security, powder room, laundry/chute, storage, plantation shutters and more. Near cafes, shops, elite schools, parklands and freeways.
